# Subscription Health Monitoring Standards

## Key Performance Indicators
- Monitor Monthly Recurring Revenue (MRR) and growth
- Track subscription churn rates (voluntary and involuntary)
- Implement cohort analysis for subscription retention
- Measure payment success rates by method/region
- Create standardized reporting intervals

## Subscription Anomaly Detection
- Implement alerting for unusual churn patterns
- Create monitoring for subscription creation failures
- Apply anomaly detection to payment failure rates
- Document response procedures for detected anomalies
- Implement proper logging for investigation

## Revenue Dashboard
- Create standardized revenue reporting views
- Implement proper revenue recognition rules
- Apply consistent metrics definitions
- Create export capabilities for financial analysis
- Document dashboard refresh frequency and data sources

## Health Indicators
- Define key subscription health indicators
- Implement trend analysis for critical metrics
- Create benchmark comparisons
- Apply proper visualization standards
- Document interpretation guidelines for indicators

## Executive Financial Dashboard
- Implement real-time MRR and ARR tracking
- Create cohort revenue analysis views
- Develop payment method performance metrics
- Visualize geographic revenue distribution
- Build executive-level summary reports

